cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.MA 

This paper is primarily focused on machine learning and explores the problem of distributed exploration in multi-armed bandits. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves collaboration and communication between multiple agents, which suggests categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves distributed computing, which suggests categories such as cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Finally, the problem being studied is specifically related to multi-armed bandits, which suggests the category cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
